dct_title_s: Chapman's new sectional map of Minnesota
dct_description_sm: "Entered according to Act of Congress in the year 1856 by Silas Chapman." "Lith. of Ferd. Mayer & Co., 96 Fulton St., N.Y." Historic Maps copy removed from cover and placed in state's flat file.
